== 分析 ==
對於第5號交響曲的音樂分析，最關鍵的問題便是「命運」動機的使用。有説法稱，上述的四音符節奏型及其變形，在后三個樂章中均有體現，起到了貫穿全曲，使之渾然一體的作用<ref>{{cite web|title=Program Notes: Celebrating Harry: Orchestral Favorites Honoring the Late Harry Ellis Dickson|url=http://www.bostonclassicalorchestra.org/program-notes/2003-2004-celebrating-harry/|accessdate=2010-04-13|publisher=Boston Classical Orchestra|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110725094233/http://www.bostonclassicalorchestra.org/program-notes/2003-2004-celebrating-harry/|archivedate=2011-07-25|deadurl=yes}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Beethoven's Fifth Symphony, Classical Notes|url=http://www.classicalnotes.net/classics/fifth.html|accessdate=2007-01-25|author=Peter Gutmann|language=en|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070124103034/http://www.classicalnotes.net/classics/fifth.html|archive-date=2007-01-24|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Beethoven's Symphony No. 5. The Destiny Symphony|url=http://www.all-about-beethoven.com/symphony5.html|accessdate=2007-01-25|publisher=All About Beethoven|language=en|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070212025710/http://www.all-about-beethoven.com/symphony5.html|archive-date=2007-02-12|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Parts of Beethoven's symphony No.5|url=http://www.symphony5.com/en/sn5.htm|accessdate=2005-11-30|language=en|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20050831060244/http://www.symphony5.com/en/sn5.htm|archivedate=2005-08-31|deadurl=yes}}</ref><ref>"Ludwig van Beethoven." ''Grove Online Encyclopedia.'' [http://www.grovemusic.com/shared/views/article.html?section=music.40026.15#music.40026.15 在綫版本]</ref>。

